name: Daniel Rey Cimafranca
text: Cramming is a personal thing.  It doesn't involve an audience ü    Yan ang topic kanina ni Manong Ted. Ibahin ang police operations sa incidents ng salvage, at bakit parang walang investigation on the salvages.  Issue on killings has to be scoped properly, hindi dapat paghaluin.
